
Folders
-------

root +
     |
     +- include    //
     |
     +- doc        Project documentation, requirements, 
     |             specifications and api documents.
     |
     +- data       Sample data files.
     |      
     +- cache      Serialized input files.        
     |
     +- src        Sources for the main application.
     |
     +- log        Log files

Building
--------

 $ make 

Requirements
------------

To build the application:

 * G++ 5.x
 * Boost Graph Library 1.60.x
 * Boost Program Options 1.60.x
 * Boost Serialization Library 1.60.x
 * xmlrpc-c 1.06.x
 * Xerces-C++ 3.1.x

 * cURLpp 0.8.x ( -lcurl )

 // tmp
 * libosmpbf-dev libprotobuf-dev ( only for OSM data )
 
To run the application:

 * Boost Program Options Shared Library 1.60.x
 * Boost Serialization Shared Library 1.60.x
 * Xerces-C++ 3.1.x

 * cURLpp 0.8.x ( -lcurl )

 // tmp
 * libosmpbf-dev libprotobuf-dev ( only for OSM data )

 ./sii_mobility source_id target_id data/PATH_TO_DATA

 ( make 2>&1 | grep --color -iP "\^|warning:|error:|" )
